promed@promedmail.org
[The clinical and epidemiological data in this news item, including
(estimated) number of cases and mortalities, are unsatisfactory; even the
infectivity of the reported condition is not certain. However, the absence
of diarrhea and lameness might allude the possible exclusion of rinderpest
and FMD. Colleagues in Punjab are invited to send more detailed clinical
observations. - Mod. AS].
